{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_11_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 莉央には内緒にしておいて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、この間撮影したリズノワドキュメンタリーの\n映像が届いたぞ。チェックしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ the footage from the LizNoir documentary\nwe filmed the other day just arrived. Take a look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、これは僕達がデビューした頃のMVだね\n今見ると恥ずかしいけど……案外悪くないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ this is the MV from when we first debuted.\nIt’s a little embarrassing to watch now… but it’s not that bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9577537311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もうリズノワは、四人でいるのが当たり前だから\n莉央さんと葵の二人きりってのは、かえって新鮮だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir being the four of you together is the norm now‚\nseeing just you and Rio-san actually feels kind of fresh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……このMV、いい出来だとは思うけど\n莉央さんとの距離が、なんだか近くないか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still… the MV is well made‚ but\naren’t you a little close to Rio-san in it…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.966666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、そういうオーダーだったんだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that’s what the order called for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4214491527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも確かに、莉央も「距離が近過ぎる！」って\nわめいて、二度も撮り直しになった覚えがあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though I do remember Rio yelling‚ “We’re too close!”\nand we had to reshoot it twice because of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、莉央が照れてるのが可愛くてさ\n僕がちょっとからかい過ぎたせいかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But seeing Rio get all flustered was cute‚\nso I might’ve teased her a bit too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0214497249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それ……例のライブ前みたいに、また喧嘩して\n三枝さんに頭抱えさせたりはしなかったよな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That didn’t turn into another fight like before that live\nand give Saegusa-san a headache again… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブと言えば、取材では話さなかったネタがあるんだ\n特別に、{user}君にだけ教えてあげるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of the live‚ there’s a story I didn’t tell in the interview.\nI’ll tell it just to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7651246071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "葵と莉央さんの昔話は、ネタに事欠かないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You never run out of stories about you and Rio-san‚ huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6317932446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.171022129
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.421022129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "あの喧嘩の後、莉央が取り計らってくれて\n衣装はさっきのかっこいいデザインに決まったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that fight‚ Rio arranged the costume\nand it ended up being that cool design from earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8876868248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの頃の僕は、どうしてもひらひらに慣れなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then I just couldn’t get used to all the frills‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.521022129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぼやきながら着替えてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I was changing while grumbling about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4876868248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そしたら莉央がズンズンこっちに歩いて来てさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Rio came marching over toward me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.621022129,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 92.621022129
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "またガミガミ小言を言われるのかと思ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought she was going to start nagging again‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3876868248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 101.1435822804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "思ったら？　……って、おい！！\nい、いきなり俺の頬を摘んで、何をするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…? —Hey!!\nW-why are you suddenly grabbing my cheek!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "こんな感じに、莉央にほっぺたをむぎゅってされた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio squished my cheeks like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6010672251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、それは分かったけどいちいち俺で\n実演してくれなくてもいいから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I get it‚ but you don’t have to\ndemonstrate it on me every time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "えー、もにもにしてて面白いのに\nまぁ莉央が真剣な顔で、僕をむぎゅむぎゅしてくるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh－ But it’s fun to squish them.\nAnyway‚ Rio kept squishing my cheeks with a serious face‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3403007507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "最初はそりゃ、呆気にとられたけど\n莉央は大真面目だし、逆にだんだん可愛く見えてきてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so at first I was pretty stunned.\nBut she was so serious that it actually started to look kind of cute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0069674174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんにそんな風に言えるのは葵だけだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re probably the only one who could say that about Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1403027216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "今にして思えば、だけど\n莉央も、僕とのコミュニケーションに悩んだんだろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking back on it now‚ though‚\nRio was probably struggling with how to communicate with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2228628635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "例の喧嘩からまだあんまり経ってなかったし\nまた、ふらっと行方不明になったらどうしようって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It hadn’t been long since that fight.\nShe might’ve been worried I’d just disappear again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.4228628635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "でもいい案もなくて、思い詰めてこう、むぎゅっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But with no better idea‚ she ended up doing this… squish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1228648344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "ま、当時はそこまで分からなかったけどね\nでも僕のことを真剣に考えてくれたのは嬉しかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I didn’t realize all that at the time.\nStill‚ I was happy she was thinking about me so seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.7895295302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "真面目くさった顔で、僕をむぎゅむぎゅしてくるのは\nシュールで面白かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way she squished my cheeks with that serious expression\nwas surreal and kind of funny.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.7895274956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どうせなら、それもインタビューで話せば良かったのに\n俺だけ聞かせてもらうのは、なんだか申し訳ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You could’ve told that story in the interview too.\nI feel bad being the only one who gets to hear it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.9000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "こんなの、わざわざ人に言うほどのことじゃないよ\nそれに莉央の可愛いとこは、僕だけ知ってればいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not something worth telling everyone.\nBesides‚ it’s enough if I’m the only one who knows Rio’s cute side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.0804342428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、莉央さんと葵は独特の絆で\n結ばれてるよなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You and Rio-san really are connected\nby a unique bond…",
        "id": ""
      },
