      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに褒められたら照れるじゃないか\n……それじゃ、僕は予定があるからそろそろ帰るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you compliment me that much‚ I’ll get embarrassed.\n…Anyway‚ I’ve got plans‚ so I should get going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.3481662908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お疲れ様\nそういや莉央さんも、今日は先約があるとか言ってたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ good work.\nCome to think of it‚ Rio-san said she had plans today too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.1666727702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "莉央と、ご飯でも食べてお泊りしようって話になってね\nちょっといいホテルを予約してあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio and I decided to grab dinner and stay over somewhere.\nI booked a pretty nice hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.8773949462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "寮だと、すぐにこころ達が乱入してきて\n二人でゆっくり思い出話も出来ないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the dorm‚ Kokoro and the others would barge in right away‚\nso we wouldn’t be able to talk about old memories in peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.3773949462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。ドキュメンタリー撮影も終わって\n疲れただろう。少しゆっくりしてきてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Now that the documentary filming is done‚\nyou must be tired. Take it easy for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.2000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_03-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "そのホテルは朝食が美味しくて有名な所でね\nモーニングのパンケーキも予約してあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That hotel is famous for its breakfast.\nI even reserved their morning pancakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.3433810073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
